  <summary date="2022-09-02T11:03:07Z" status="Introduced in House">VA Same-Day Scheduling Act of 2022

This bill requires the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to ensure that when a veteran enrolled in the VA health care system contacts the VA by telephone to schedule an appointment for care or services at a VA facility, the scheduling for the appointment occurs during that telephone call.</summary>
